    "rich_text_q4ed7V": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "text_block_YrcCYz": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "",
            "title_heading": false,
            "accordion_enabled": false,
            "text": "<p>Whether you’re swimming laps, chasing waves, or lounging poolside, our sustainable triangle bikinis are designed to stay put, so you can move without adjusting. Adjustable straps and ties allow you to customise your fit, while our seamless, double-lined construction ensures a smooth, flattering silhouette from every angle.</p><p>From surf-friendly triangle bikinis that won’t shift in the waves to minimalist summer bikinis for relaxed beach days, this collection offers the perfect balance of function and style. And because each piece is consciously made in Bali, you can feel good knowing your purchase supports fair wages, ethical production, and low-waste manufacturing.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "center": true,
            "block_width": 100,
            "accordion_icon_color": "#000000",
            "accordion_icon_size": 20
          }
        }
