    "image_with_text_CwNMMR": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "name": "Image with text",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/by_imanperdana_-_Gili_Midnight_-_2023-7.jpg",
        "image_position": "left",
        "image_size": "medium",
        "image_height": "fixed",
        "desktop_image_height": 450,
        "mobile_image_height": 450,
        "title": "Why Choose Our Triangle Bikinis?",
        "text": "<p>Not all triangle bikinis are created equal. While most are designed for lounging, ours are engineered for movement, durability, and comfort - without compromising on style. Here’s what sets them apart:</p><p>The classic triangle cut highlights your natural curves, while adjustable ties at the neck and back let you control your coverage and fit.<br/></p><p>Double lining and quality construction mean your bikini stays in place, whether you’re diving into the pool or paddling out for a surf.<br/></p><p>Made from premium Italian recycled fabric, these bikinis are as kind to the planet as they are to your skin.<br/></p><p>Built-in sun protection helps shield your skin from harmful UV rays, letting you enjoy longer days outdoors.<br/></p><p>Designed to mix and match with our <a href=\"https://oceansoulbali.com/collections/bikini-bottoms\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://oceansoulbali.com/collections/bikini-bottoms\">bikini bottoms</a>, <a href=\"https://oceansoulbali.com/collections/womens-rash-vest\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://oceansoulbali.com/collections/womens-rash-vest\">rash vests</a>, and <a href=\"https://oceansoulbali.com/collections/beach-accessories/products/surf-shorts\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://oceansoulbali.com/collections/beach-accessories/products/surf-shorts\">surf shorts </a>for a look that’s uniquely yours.</p>",
        "button_text": "Button",
        "link": "",
        "center_align": true,
        "text_color": "#606060",
        "background_color": "#f7f7f7"
      }
    },
    "image_with_text_TaKYpw": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "name": "Image with text",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/Berawa_8andco_digital_-_Gili_Blush_Pink_-_2022-74.jpg",
        "image_position": "right",
        "image_size": "medium",
        "image_height": "fixed",
        "desktop_image_height": 450,
        "mobile_image_height": 450,
        "title": "Sustainable Swimwear, Ethically Made",
        "text": "<p>At Ocean Soul Swimwear, sustainability is more than just a buzzword. Every eco-friendly triangle bikini in this collection is crafted with the planet in mind:</p><p>Each suit is made using regenerated nylon from ocean waste, such as discarded fishing nets and fabric scraps.<br/></p><p>We produce in small batches to minimise waste and avoid overproduction.<br/></p><p>Every bikini is made locally in Bali by skilled artisans who are paid fair wages.<br/></p><p>By choosing a sustainable triangle bikini, you’re making a conscious decision to reduce your environmental impact while supporting ethical production practices.</p>",
        "button_text": "Button",
        "link": "",
        "center_align": true,
        "text_color": "#606060",
        "background_color": "#f7f7f7"
      }
    },
    "image_with_text_cfJHP8": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "name": "Image with text",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/1G0A8366_wildtravelingsoul_1.jpg",
        "image_position": "left",
        "image_size": "medium",
        "image_height": "fixed",
        "desktop_image_height": 450,
        "mobile_image_height": 450,
        "title": "Performance Meets Style",
        "text": "<p>Our triangle bikinis are designed for women who want it all - support, style, and sustainability. They transition seamlessly from the surf to the sand, giving you a bikini top that’s just as comfortable under a wetsuit as it is under the sun.</p><p>Tested in real waves to ensure minimal movement and maximum comfort.<br/></p><p>Ideal for both saltwater and poolside wear, retaining its shape and colour over time.<br/></p><p>Perfect for all-day wear, so you can go from water to café without feeling damp or uncomfortable.</p>",
        "button_text": "Button",
        "link": "",
        "center_align": true,
        "text_color": "#606060",
        "background_color": "#f7f7f7"
