        "heading": "How to Style Your Triangle Bikini",
        "subheading_text": "<p>The beauty of a triangle bikini lies in its versatility. </p><p>Active Days: Pair your bikini top with matching <a href=\"/products/surf-shorts\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Surf Shorts | The Sabu Surf Short\">surf shorts</a> or a <a href=\"/collections/womens-rash-vest\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Womens Rash Vest\">women’s rash vest</a> for extra sun protection and security in the water.<br/>Relaxed Beach Days: Wear with minimal coverage bikini bottoms and a breezy kaftan for a laid-back summer look.</p><p>Mix & Match: Combine with contrasting bikini bottoms for a unique, personalised style that reflects your mood.</p>",
        "button_text": "Button",
